nhc_headline: ...JULIETTE FADING AS IT MOVES INTO THE COOL OCEAN WATERS OF THE EASTERN NORTH PACIFIC...
summary: ...JULIETTE FADING AS IT MOVES INTO THE COOL OCEAN WATERS OF THE EASTERN NORTH PACIFIC... As of 2:00 AM PDT Wed Aug 27 the center of Juliette was located near 21.9, -118.8 with movement NNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
